{
  "stem": "21786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, downtown, in the old Jewish section-- which is, I mean, nowadays the center of the attention of anybody who is a visitor to Prague-- is the old Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there are literally four synagogues within the radius of 200 meters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of them is from the 12th century, a very stern building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of them is the synagogue where there are the names of all the deceased.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There are about 90,000 names on the walls of all the Jews from the Czech and Moravian lands who died during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then one of them was changed to a museum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in that is wedged an old Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That is from 14th, 15th century.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there is lying the famous Rabbi Low, L-O-W, who made the miracle of creating a golem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was kept by the Nazis, under the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They left there, even, a clock with Jewish lettering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It-- the clock goes anti-clockwise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were gathering all of the kinds of religious objects from all the lands, and brought it to Prague and threw it into one of the synagogues-- all the books or all the Torahs.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "For they wanted, after the war, to show the world that it is not so bad, that they are-- have got still a kind of human philanthropic trend.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The wanted to create there a museum of extinct people, using this part, this section, of the city for it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 16 years old at that point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The kind of restrictions which, already, the Germans, the Nazis, tested in Germany and in Austria-- obviously which was occupied exactly one year prior to that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they implied all the laws and bylaws concerning Jews, literally within 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
